{"tid":1672660,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蔣麗芸：不排除動議曾經出席暴亂活動議員減薪一半","createTime":"2019-10-24T08:44:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T13:48:50.000Z","uid":200758,"like":18,"dislike":438,"uniUserReply":126,"replies":[{"pid":"b52b23c793f055485a28269202630ed8fd81faa2","tid":1672660,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T08:44:49.000Z","msg":"立法會續會，恢復二讀辯論《2019年稅務(修訂)(稅務寬免)條例草案》，涉及一次性寬減75%薪俸稅、利得稅及個人入息課稅，上限20000元，政府提出修正案，建議寬減至100%。<br />\n<br />\n多名建制派議員發言，並談及反修例示威運動。民建聯蔣麗芸表示，不排除提出動議，建議出席過暴亂活動、支持暴徒的議員，要減一半薪酬。議員陳凱欣說，中產人士生活開支龐大，但政府提出的一次性派糖成效短暫，不能單靠派糖撲火，挽回市民對政府的不信任，因此建議設立家庭傭工免稅額及子女教育開支免稅額，紓緩中產家庭負擔。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨的楊岳橋說，政府建議提升稅務寬減百分比，但沒有調節扣稅金額上限，難以讓收入較高的中產人士釋放更多消費力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488010-20191024.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488010-20191024.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUocg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=da7a0a50\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488010-20191024.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=2e54547f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488010-20191024.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"c03bd87f03892fa211f967b8a26954b7e4e2f6b7","tid":1672660,"uid":12628,"like":538,"dislike":0,"score":538,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T08:46:06.000Z","msg":"不排除動議智商不足40的議員減薪9成！"},{"pid":"e34cd5aa819c7dce8d7caa730867cab0e56563bf","tid":1672660,"uid":53498,"like":188,"dislike":0,"score":188,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T08:46:25.000Z","msg":"不排除光復香港後,誅保蝗九族,兼且切片當韓國燒烤"},{"pid":"9ec469703ef8702ae56b72b83f2616dc3f7f1b17","tid":1672660,"uid":253573,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T08:46:33.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"4c9d4b95b00d89e0003a17bb37c33459082bdbda","tid":1672660,"uid":53019,"like":78,"dislike":0,"score":78,"quote":{"pid":"c03bd87f03892fa211f967b8a26954b7e4e2f6b7","tid":1672660,"uid":12628,"like":538,"dislike":0,"score":538,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T08:46:06.000Z","msg":"不排除動議智商不足40的議員減薪9成！"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T08:47:12.000Z","msg":"炒 L 佢啦！ 仲扣人工？！"},{"pid":"65b927d813ad82b3a89a7d9071748fe416217507","tid":1672660,"uid":265192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T08:47:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">中共斥巨資收賣西方<br />\n遊說集團統戰華盛頓</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n【華為被禁】華為遊說費飆60倍！原來聘用特朗普籌款人 欲說服白宮<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2479940%3Fr%3Dcpsdlc&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUocg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=b438d78d\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc</a><br />\n<br />\n董建華基金會 擲2,240萬左右美政策<br />\n大搞政治游說 否認中共代理人<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUocg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=de26b4eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&h=11b362ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">抗衡中國魔掌<br />\n組建香港既遊說團隊！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">誠意推薦：</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港大專學界國際事務代表團眾籌計劃</em></strong><br />\nHong Kong IAD Crowdfunding Plan<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUocg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=11dd04fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港眾志國際眾籌計劃 Demosisto International Campaign Crowdfunding Project</em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUocg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=8535f884\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">什麼是遊說集團？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">遊說集團的工作，<strong><ins>是嘗試影響立法者</ins></strong>或其他持份者決定或行為，在政治角力中為服務對象<strong><ins>爭取利益</ins></strong>。遊說集團的服務對象，可以是國家、企業、社會團體、個人。在美國，政治遊說是極為普遍及重要的一環；幾乎所有政治操作都有遊說集團的參與。</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">為什麼香港需要遊說隊伍？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">任何國家的政治，背後都擁有複雜的政治脈絡；包括國家政策、政治形勢、民意、錯綜複雜的利益網絡、乃至個別官員或議員的性情喜好。要在國際社會維護和爭取香港的利益，<strong><ins>香港需要一支能具經驗和技巧，能夠有效收風、熟識政治形勢</ins></strong>、具備遊說策略的隊伍。</span>"},{"pid":"bfac17de97ee5b03ef7266fad38d8c73ef97ff6b","tid":1672660,"uid":133412,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T08:48:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢係以柒見稱嘅議員"},{"pid":"3404e34452810ee728e3153c9a3d83a25c10e00f","tid":1672660,"uid":265449,"like":1,"dislike":6,"sc